<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Revenue Recovery System – Never Lose a Lead Again</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f9fafc; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; color: #1e293b; }
    h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4361ee 0%, #3046c0 100%); color: white; padding: 80px 0; margin-bottom: 60px; }
    .hero h1 { color: white; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 20px 0 30px; opacity: 0.9; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: white; color: #4361ee; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 40px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.2s; }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .btn-outline { background: transparent; border: 2px solid white; color: white; }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: white; color: #4361ee; }
    .features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin: 60px 0; }
    .feature-card { background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); text-align: center; }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 20px 0 10px; color: #1e293b; }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 3rem; }
    .steps { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin: 60px 0; }
    .step { flex: 1 1 200px; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
    .step-number { background: #4361ee; color: white; width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .pricing-cta { background: white; text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); margin: 60px 0; }
    .pricing-cta h3 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .testimonial { background: #f0f4ff; padding: 60px 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 60px 0; text-align: center; }
    .testimonial p { font-size: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .testimonial-author { margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .hero { padding: 60px 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- Hero Section (UPDATED with Try Live Demo) -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Turn Missed Calls Into Revenue</h1>
      <p>AI‑powered voicemail transcription, lead intelligence, and instant recovery – so you never lose a customer.</p>
      <a href="/demo" class="btn">Try Live Demo</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline">View Plans</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Everything You Need to Recover Lost Leads</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎙️</div>
        <h3>Call Capture</h3>
        <p>Every missed call is transcribed and analyzed in real time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>AI Lead Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Extract name, service, urgency, and estimated value automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Revenue Tracking</h3>
        <p>See exactly how much money you're leaving on the table.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
        <h3>SMS Auto‑Reply</h3>
        <p>Instantly engage callers with a text message while they leave a voicemail.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>Missed Call</h3>
        <p>Customer calls, you miss it – voicemail is captured.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>AI Transcription</h3>
        <p>We transcribe and extract key details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Lead Alert</h3>
        <p>You get the lead in your dashboard and via SMS.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <h3>Close the Deal</h3>
        <p>Respond fast and convert.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pricing Summary (removed free trial mention) -->
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing-cta">
      <h3>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h3>
      <p>Choose the plan that fits your business. <a href="/demo">Try the demo</a> to see it in action.</p>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn" style="background:#4361ee; color:white;">See Plans & Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonial">
      <p>"Since using Revenue Recovery System, we've recovered over $5,000 in missed opportunities. A game changer!"</p>
      <div class="testimonial-author">– Jamie, Lawn Care Pro</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>